{"tid":635084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"邊餵乳邊啪啪！ 媽媽極樂狂搖兒子暈","createTime":"2018-04-19T23:45:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T02:12:21.000Z","uid":45772,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7a73ea0d4da2daa75dab14c528814f82dcd8c68a","tid":635084,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:45:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/life/398984\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nextmag.com.tw%2Fbreakingnews%2Flife%2F398984&d=pPF0LqDv7Rk1lMHRQ1CaJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6d5cc8b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nextmag.com.tw/breakingnews/life/398984</a><br />\n<br />\n不少媽媽都堅持要親自餵母乳，不僅能讓孩子身體健康，也增進親子關係，但最近網路上流傳一部影片，只見媽媽正跨坐在老公腰上，不停上下搖動，但兒子卻還在一邊吸奶，直接三個人同步進行，父母似乎也不在意兒子就在一旁，直接上演激烈動作片，引起網友批評「有那麼急嗎？」。<br />\n<br />\n網友們紛紛表示，「別教壞小孩呀！雖然孩子年紀小，但這行為還是不適當」、「小孩雖不懂，看到多少還是有心理影響」、「等孩子睡了再做很難嘛？」、「這孩子未來很有性發展前途」、「其實爸媽正在啟發兒子」、「蠟筆小新是這樣來的」。（編輯/數位發展部）"},{"pid":"49a41af5d9e79700a43d1bcd492418a5b5efd424","tid":635084,"uid":150098,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:47:07.000Z","msg":"睇到標題，已覺得痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7b0d3ccff67cf1df9f4c26d550149c889c31da","tid":635084,"uid":154738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:47:44.000Z","msg":"Av"},{"pid":"30d9d3b3bf1e7705c7909b4525ac330fd29df294","tid":635084,"uid":64318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:49:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以話</span></span>"},{"pid":"129ea22e68980bd2d56a39247bd03df72a8a5443","tid":635084,"uid":50328,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:50:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2c2f75e003f46a294bdf27abcc24fbd211442502","tid":635084,"uid":3870,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T23:50:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">網路上流傳</span>"},{"pid":"7